# Toy MLIR

The toy language from the LLVM MLIR tutorial.


## Get Started

```sh
MLIR_SRC_ROOT=<PATH_TO_MLIR> make
```
Where `MLIR_SRC_ROOT` is the path to the MLIR source in the LLVM project  -- i.e. `mlir` subdirectory in [github.com/llvm/llvm-project](https://github.com/llvm/llvm-project/tree/main/mlir).